@end

- Flying Slash is now light melee damage rather than spirit
- Flying Slash slow increased from -30% to -50%
- Flying Slash cooldown increased from 21s to 36s
- Flying Slash range increased from 20m to 25m
- Flying Slash T1 changed from "25% Slow" to "-18s Cooldown"
- Flying Slash T2 changed from "+20m Cast Range" to "+20m Cast Range and gain +40 Spirit for 6s"
- Flying Slash T3 changed from "Can Grapple to ally heroes and +6 Weapon Damage for 10s" to "Can Grapple to ally heroes. Becomes Charged and grants +2 charges (3s between charges)."

- Fixed Flying Slash T3 ally cast stopping too soon before reaching the player

